  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK548">
<l>eṇpatattā ṉāṭi muṟaiceyyā maṉṉavaṉ </l>
<l> ṟaṇpatattāṟ ṟāṉē keṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The king who gives not facile audience (to those who approach him), and who does not examine and pass judgment (on their complaints), will perish in disgrace.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
